# рџљЂ AI Resume Screening System (ResumeIQ)

An AI-powered Applicant Tracking System (ATS) that automatically parses, analyzes, and ranks resumes against a Job Description using Natural Language Processing (NLP) and Sentence Transformers.

Built with **FastAPI**, **React (Vite)**, **SQLite**, and **Sentence Transformers**, ResumeIQ helps recruiters quickly identify the most suitable candidates by evaluating semantic similarity, skills, education, experience, and eligibility.

---

