# рџ§  AI Ranking Algorithm

The ranking engine evaluates candidates using multiple parameters.

| Parameter | Weight |
|-----------|---------|
| Semantic Similarity | 30% |
| Skill Match | 35% |
| Education Match | 5% |
| Experience Match | 15% |
| Eligibility Match | 15% |

The final score is calculated as:

```
Final Score =
0.30 Г— Similarity +
0.35 Г— Skill Score +
0.05 Г— Education Score +
0.15 Г— Experience Score +
0.15 Г— Eligibility Score
```

